subscribers with a $200 Azure credit,

39
00:01:31,755 --> 00:01:33,050
that they can use for Azure

40
00:01:33,050 --> 00:01:35,585
paid products during
a 30-day trial period.

41
00:01:35,585 --> 00:01:39,040
Once you use that $200 credit
or reach your trials end,

42
